---
// Componente About
---

<section id="about" class="section py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        <span class="text-primary">Sobre</span> Mí
      </h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full mb-8"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Marco decorativo -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-primary rounded-lg transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4"></div>
          
          <!-- Card principal -->
          <div class="relative z-10 bg-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-800">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text">Perfil Profesional</h3>
              
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Soy un Desarrollador FullStack recién graduado de DAM (Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma) y técnico en SIR/SMX con 2.5 años de experiencia en Barcelona.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Actualmente trabajo como Desarrollador FullStack Intern en AgriNews, donde me estoy formando en .NET, IA y backend. Mi objetivo es seguir creciendo profesionalmente y aportar soluciones innovadoras.
              </p>
              
              <div class="pt-4">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Mis habilidades incluyen:</h4>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>.NET</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>React</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>Laravel</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>Tailwind CSS</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>IA</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                    <span>Java</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:bg-primary/40 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Experiencia laboral</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 pl-16">
              2.5 años de experiencia como desarrollador y administrador de sistemas, trabajando en diversas empresas y proyectos.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:bg-primary/40 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z" />
                  <path d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14zm-4 6v-7.5l4-2.222" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Formación académica</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 pl-16">
              Graduado en Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma (DAM) y técnico en Sistemas y Redes.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:bg-primary/40 transition-colors duration-300">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Objetivos profesionales</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 pl-16">
              Especializarme en desarrollo full stack con tecnologías modernas, profundizando en la integración de IA en aplicaciones web.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 